<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Event Management</title>
    <!-- Link to Google Fonts or other custom font -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Montserrat:wght@400;700&display=swap">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
            background-color: #1f1f1f; /* Dark background for contrast */
            color: #f4f4f9; /* Light text for contrast */
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 3rem;
            text-align: center;
            color: #ff4500; /* A vibrant orange for heading contrast */
            margin-bottom: 40px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 3px;
        }

        .steps-container {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 40px;
        }

        .step {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #2c2c2c;
            border-radius: 15px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
        }

        .step:nth-child(odd) {
            flex-direction: row-reverse; /* Reverse for odd steps */
        }

        .step img {
            width: 150px;
            height: auto;
            margin: 0 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
        }

        .step-content {
            flex: 1;
        }

        .step h2 {
            font-size: 1.8rem;
            color: #ffb400; /* Bright orange for subheadings */
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .step p {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        /* Responsive adjustments */
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .step {
                flex-direction: column;
                text-align: center;
            }

            .step img {
                margin-bottom: 20px;
                width: 80%;
            }

            .step:nth-child(odd) {
                flex-direction: column;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Event Management Services</h1>

        <div class="steps-container">
            <!-- Step 1: Planning and Strategy -->
            <div class="step">
                <img src="public/images/eventmgmt.png" alt="Planning and Strategy Image">
                <div class="step-content">
                    <h2>Step 1: Planning and Strategy</h2>
                    <p>Our experienced team ensures every event starts with thorough planning. We create a blueprint tailored to your objectives, ensuring flawless execution down the road.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Step 2: Design and Creative Execution -->
            <div class="step">
                <img src="https://example.com/design-image.jpg" alt="Design and Creative Execution Image">
                <div class="step-content">
                    <h2>Step 2: Design and Creative Execution</h2>
                    <p>From concept to creation, we handle the design and execution of your event, ensuring every detail reflects your vision and brand.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Step 3: Event Coordination -->
            <div class="step">
                <img src="https://example.com/coordination-image.jpg" alt="Event Coordination Image">
                <div class="step-content">
                    <h2>Step 3: Event Coordination</h2>
                    <p>On the day of the event, our team takes care of coordination, ensuring everything runs smoothly from start to finish.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Step 4: Post-Event Support -->
            <div class="step">
                <img src="https://example.com/post-event-image.jpg" alt="Post-Event Support Image">
                <div class="step-content">
                    <h2>Step 4: Post-Event Support</h2>
                    <p>After the event, we provide full post-event support, ensuring follow-up tasks are handled with the same care as the event itself.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>
